<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title><%= subject %></title>
  <style>
    /* Dark modern theme inspired by The VIP Studio dashboard */

    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: 'Inter', 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #0d0f16; /* Dark background */
      color: #e5e7eb; /* Light text */
    }

    .email-container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #151821; /* Slightly lighter dark */
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .header {
      background-color: #fcd45b; /* Yellow header */
      color: #0d0f16;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 25px 20px;
    }

    .header h1 {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .content {
      padding: 30px;
    }

    .content p {
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #d1d5db;
    }

    .invite-card {
      background-color: #1f232d;
      border: 1px solid #2d313d;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 25px 0;
    }

    .info-item {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 10px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #2d313d;
    }

    .info-item:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
    }

    .label {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #fcd45b;
    }

    .value {
      color: #e5e7eb;
    }

    .invite-link {
      word-break: break-all;
      background: #facc1530;
      padding: 8px 12px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      border: 1px solid #fcd45b;
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 14px;
      margin-top: 10px;
      display: none; /* Hide the link display */
    }

    .warning {
      background-color: #1f232d;
      border-left: 4px solid #fcd45b;
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 12px 15px;
      margin-top: 20px;
      color: #fcd45b;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .cta-button {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 30px 0;
    }

    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #fcd45b;
      color: #0d0f16;
      padding: 12px 30px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      border-radius: 10px;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    .button:hover {
      background-color: #eab308;
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(252, 212, 91, 0.3);
    }

    .footer {
      background-color: #11131a;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #2d313d;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #9ca3af;
    }

    .footer a {
      color: #fcd45b;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .button-container {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 25px 0;
    }

    .alternative-text {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #9ca3af;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .copy-instruction {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #9ca3af;
      margin-top: 15px;
      font-style: italic;
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .info-item {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: flex-start;
      }

      .value {
        margin-top: 5px;
      }

      .button {
        padding: 14px 30px;
        font-size: 15px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Welcome to <%= companyName %>!</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <p>Hey <strong><%= name %></strong>,</p>
      <p>You've been invited to join <strong><%= companyName %></strong> as a <strong><%= roleName %></strong>. Click the button below to set your password and get started:</p>

      <div class="invite-card">
        <div class="info-item">
          <span class="label">Your Role:</span>
          <span class="value"><%= roleName %></span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-item">
          <span class="label">Email:</span>
          <span class="value"><%= email %></span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="warning">
        ⚠️ This invitation link will expire in 24 hours. Please set your password immediately.
      </div>

      <div class="cta-button">
        <a href="<%= inviteLink %>" class="button" target="_blank">Set Your Password & Get Started</a>
      </div>

      <p>If you didn't expect this invitation or face any issues, please contact your administrator.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>Best regards,<br><strong>The <%= companyName %> Team</strong></p>
      <p><a href="<%= websiteUrl %>"><%= websiteUrl %></a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>